name: Shance Adams
description:
i am SHANCEA at You Are Hot On Out in america.add the capital letters together and get back to me.let’s see how smart you are.
My values are very important to me. I want to find someone who also shares those values.
I am thankful for the life I have and the family I share it with. Family is important to me. I like sports (played high school and college baseball ). I like going to sporting events when I have a chance.
I am very passionate about a lot of things. I put a lot of emphasis into my goals. I pretty much live a healthy lifestyle, eat healthy and work out. I love my family and friends and look forward to finding my best friend and soul mate. I spend most of my time hanging out with family, friends, going to the beach, watching movies, trying new things, and trying to enjoy life.
I am a Beautician and I love what I do. I also am involved in some volunteer/service type things throughout the year. I like to go out to dinner and the movies but sometimes I like just staying in and relaxing at home.
